726514f-b.text:
Dry Harbor Road, west side, at 82nd Street. This house is in the line of 82nd Street at its point of intersection with Dry Harbor Road. Mrs. Seits or Seites was the owner in 1873. The later view of this set shows the building being repaired.
1923
View 2: May 1926
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
